1
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,720
[1909]

2
00:02:01,536 --> 00:02:02,800
Thank you, Phob.

3
00:02:04,299 --> 00:02:05,600
(In unison) Let's go.

4
00:02:06,896 --> 00:02:07,897
Go straight.

5
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,040
[1921 (12 years later)]

6
00:02:13,595 --> 00:02:17,040
Definite rules for spacing are not successful,

7
00:02:17,739 --> 00:02:20,480
it is a matter of a draftsman's judgement

8
00:02:20,747 --> 00:02:22,250
and sense of design.

9
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:37,880
I'd like to give a cotton rose to you, Your Highness.

10
00:02:40,472 --> 00:02:41,473
Sure, you can.

11
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,281
I should tuck it behind your ear.

12
00:02:46,576 --> 00:02:48,400
- No!
- Why not?

13
00:02:48,619 --> 00:02:49,960
It doesn't suit me, it suits you.

14
00:02:51,407 --> 00:02:52,480
It looks better on you.

15
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,320
Come on.

16
00:02:56,747 --> 00:02:57,920
So adorable.

17
00:02:58,640 --> 00:03:01,080
- I don't think so.
- Of course, it is.

18
00:03:02,363 --> 00:03:05,120
Stop touching it already. Stop, okay?

19
00:03:06,238 --> 00:03:08,760
Stop fidgeting already. Stay still like this.

20
00:03:09,859 --> 00:03:12,160
- I can't take it off?
- No, you can't. Just put it like that.

21
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,560
[Varakulvatin Palace]

22
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,001
Hey! All of you!

23
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:35,440
Stop running around like monkeys!

24
00:03:36,027 --> 00:03:39,200
He has gifts for eveyone.

25
00:03:41,451 --> 00:03:43,280
Euam, well…

26
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:46,040
why are they giving us gifts?

27
00:03:46,424 --> 00:03:47,920
It's not even Songkran.

28
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:51,200
Well, Prince Vasin just got promoted

29
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:56,900
so they're kind enough to give something to us.

30
00:03:57,827 --> 00:03:59,880
We're so lucky

31
00:04:00,003 --> 00:04:01,680
to have kind masters like them.

32
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,560
Sathu.

33
00:04:05,774 --> 00:04:07,560
What are you waiting for? Come on.

34
00:04:22,174 --> 00:04:23,360
Thank you, Your Highness.

35
00:04:24,958 --> 00:04:29,000
Nual, where is your son?

36
00:04:29,384 --> 00:04:30,960
Call him for me.

37
00:04:31,347 --> 00:04:32,920
I have something f or him.

38
00:04:34,630 --> 00:04:37,520
Phob is hanging out with Prince Tinnakorn for sure.

39
00:04:37,936 --> 00:04:41,480
When you see Prince Tinnakorn, you will see Phob there.

40
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:45,960
Just like me, waiting to serve you, Your Highness.

41
00:04:46,056 --> 00:04:47,057
Stop it.

42
00:04:50,142 --> 00:04:51,920
Why don't you call him for me?

43
00:04:53,064 --> 00:04:54,065
Yes, Your Highness.

44
00:05:05,803 --> 00:05:07,515
- Watch out!
- I'm okay.

45
00:05:09,406 --> 00:05:10,200
Please be careful, Your Highness.

46
00:05:11,566 --> 00:05:13,240
I think I should get it for you.

47
00:05:13,614 --> 00:05:15,240
Why are you yelling?

48
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:18,628
Be careful. There are many flowers,

49
00:05:19,054 --> 00:05:20,600
why do you want that one?

50
00:05:20,865 --> 00:05:22,680
I like this one.

51
00:05:23,606 --> 00:05:24,607
Watch out.

52
00:05:35,262 --> 00:05:36,263
Phob!

53
00:05:41,019 --> 00:05:43,360
Stay still, I will clean it for you.

54
00:05:55,369 --> 00:05:56,370
Can you wipe it off?

55
00:05:57,624 --> 00:05:58,625
Sure, I can.

56
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,560
I was so worried about you

57
00:06:07,171 --> 00:06:08,400
and you made fun of my face.

58
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,521
You're so mean.

59
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:13,200
You looked funny when you fell.

60
00:06:16,142 --> 00:06:17,600
Stop sulking already.

61
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,241
Smile.

62
00:06:25,902 --> 00:06:28,320
Smile. Stop making grumpy face already.

63
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:34,080
Smile, come on. Wider.

64
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:37,360
- I got more on me.
- Phob.

65
00:06:42,198 --> 00:06:43,600
Princess is calling for you.

66
00:06:45,179 --> 00:06:46,180
Okay, Mom.

67
00:06:56,342 --> 00:06:58,182
I met Khun Luang Prat yesterday.

68
00:06:58,683 --> 00:07:00,800
Your teacher said that you're a bright student.

69
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,940
You're a fast learner. You've doen so well in school.

70
00:07:10,048 --> 00:07:12,100
Thank you, Your Highness,

71
00:07:12,917 --> 00:07:15,307
for allowing my son to study.

72
00:07:25,270 --> 00:07:27,654
Your son is a bright student.

73
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:30,880
My son and I talked

74
00:07:30,923 --> 00:07:34,280
and we decided to pay for his tuition fee as long as he wants.

75
00:07:34,619 --> 00:07:38,475
We wish that he won't have to serve us in the future.

76
00:07:39,974 --> 00:07:42,040
Instead, he should serve the nation.

77
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,840
Thank you, Your Highness.

78
00:07:53,075 --> 00:07:55,520
Phob is doing so well in school, Dad and Grandma.

79
00:07:55,934 --> 00:07:59,320
He always helped me with the lessons.

80
00:08:00,718 --> 00:08:02,840
No matter how good he is, he still is a servant.

81
00:08:03,512 --> 00:08:05,000
He was born in a lower class of society so he still needs to crawl.

82
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:10,720
You can give him more pens but you can't change his servant blood.

83
00:08:11,358 --> 00:08:12,640
Tin, you should have known better.

84
00:08:12,897 --> 00:08:14,700
Don't praise him too much or he would get cocky.

85
00:08:15,134 --> 00:08:16,600
I'm just telling the truth.

86
00:08:17,278 --> 00:08:19,160
Actually, you should let him

87
00:08:19,395 --> 00:08:21,522
tutor you sometimes

88
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:23,500
- so you'd do better in school.
- Tin!

89
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:26,000
If you don't have nice thing to say, then keep your mouth shut.

90
00:08:26,904 --> 00:08:29,971
You're doing nothing but getting off track.

91
00:08:30,376 --> 00:08:32,040
You're bringing shame to the family.

92
00:08:33,446 --> 00:08:35,440
You won't study, you don't care about reading books.

93
00:08:35,926 --> 00:08:37,286
Since you were young until now,

94
00:08:37,392 --> 00:08:39,600
can you be as good as the servant's son?

95
00:08:51,830 --> 00:08:52,831
Phob,

96
00:08:53,526 --> 00:08:55,451
don't mind Chat.

97
00:08:55,579 --> 00:08:57,062
But what he said is true.

98
00:08:57,648 --> 00:08:59,049
Who cares if I'm doing great in school?

99
00:09:00,886 --> 00:09:02,280
I can only be a servant,

100
00:09:03,398 --> 00:09:04,399
a lower class of the society.

101
00:09:05,035 --> 00:09:06,036
Phob.

102
00:09:21,267 --> 00:09:22,268
Look at this.

103
00:09:27,246 --> 00:09:28,247
A cotton rose

104
00:09:30,019 --> 00:09:31,624
is white in the morning,

105
00:09:32,408 --> 00:09:34,060
then it changes to pink at noon.

106
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,720
And in the evening, it won't be the same anymore.

107
00:09:41,448 --> 00:09:44,920
In the future, your status can be different based on your competency.

108
00:09:46,838 --> 00:09:48,200
Nothing can stop you.

109
00:09:50,112 --> 00:09:53,000
You're determined and focused.

110
00:09:53,987 --> 00:09:55,160
I believe in you.

111
00:10:03,406 --> 00:10:04,480
Thank you, Your Highness.

112
00:10:08,107 --> 00:10:09,160
You've been so nice to me

113
00:10:10,982 --> 00:10:12,440
since we were young.

114
00:10:14,022 --> 00:10:15,023
You've never once see me

115
00:10:16,198 --> 00:10:17,520
as a servant.

116
00:10:18,416 --> 00:10:19,880
You've never disdained me.

117
00:10:21,558 --> 00:10:22,559
Therefore,

118
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:29,160
I don't care what the future holds,

119
00:10:35,142 --> 00:10:36,800
I will be your Phob

120
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:40,200
forever and ever.

121
00:10:49,601 --> 00:10:50,960
Now you're saying a nice thing to me.

122
00:10:52,432 --> 00:10:54,742
But I will study in the UK in two months.

123
00:10:55,859 --> 00:10:58,640
By then you might be happy

124
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:01,640
that you don’t have to follow me around anymore.

125
00:11:04,664 --> 00:11:05,880
- Your Highness.
- Phob.

126
00:11:11,824 --> 00:11:13,440
- Stop it!
- Stay away.

127
00:11:14,171 --> 00:11:15,680
- Your Highness!
- Come here.

128
00:11:18,832 --> 00:11:21,100
My dad scolded me because of you, you stupid servant!

129
00:11:21,520 --> 00:11:23,900
He sent you to school so you could serve me.

130
00:11:23,921 --> 00:11:25,320
Instead, you chose to be a star.

131
00:11:25,635 --> 00:11:28,800
You didn't know your place, you're just little dust under my feet.

132
00:11:29,374 --> 00:11:31,360
You hear me! Get out!

133
00:11:41,375 --> 00:11:42,440
You stupid servant!

134
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:46,200
You hurt me? I'm going to kill you.

135
00:11:46,582 --> 00:11:48,720
What is going on? What is this?

136
00:11:48,883 --> 00:11:50,884
- What?
- Grandma!

137
00:11:50,976 --> 00:11:53,720
He hurt me! Look at this! He hurt me!

138
00:11:53,787 --> 00:11:54,923
He hurt me!

139
00:11:54,982 --> 00:11:57,000
How did you raise him to be like this?

140
00:11:57,315 --> 00:11:59,760
I'm hurt! This is so painful.

141
00:12:00,248 --> 00:12:01,249
Grandma!

142
00:12:01,598 --> 00:12:04,600
Look at me! Why don't you look at me now?

143
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,920
You have to look at me!

144
00:12:17,267 --> 00:12:20,579
Prince Wasin and Princess Pattamapreeya were kind to you

145
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:23,400
and I still need to punish you so you will remember this.

146
00:12:27,592 --> 00:12:29,342
But Prince Chatthorn hurt Prince Tinnakorn first.

147
00:12:30,142 --> 00:12:32,093
I just protected my prince.

148
00:12:33,811 --> 00:12:34,840
Prince Chatthorn

149
00:12:35,336 --> 00:12:37,200
started the whole thing.

150
00:12:39,763 --> 00:12:41,486
Are you talking back to me?

151
00:12:41,806 --> 00:12:44,632
Why didn't you know your place? We're just servants.

152
00:12:44,923 --> 00:12:46,700
Why did you become so full of yourself?

153
00:12:47,779 --> 00:12:51,000
Your grandma was a servant in the palace.

154
00:12:51,694 --> 00:12:53,600
And I was born here.

155
00:12:54,451 --> 00:12:57,040
We can live like this

156
00:12:57,100 --> 00:12:58,832
because our masters are so kind to us.

157
00:12:58,976 --> 00:13:00,864
But there is no more slavery for a really long time.

158
00:13:01,792 --> 00:13:03,462
I am grateful for them.

159
00:13:03,867 --> 00:13:06,635
But what he did was wrong and it was different.

160
00:13:07,435 --> 00:13:10,123
You wanted me to be responsible for what I didn't do?

161
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:13,741
Only the masters can do no wrong?

162
00:13:14,347 --> 00:13:15,348
Phob!

163
00:13:17,091 --> 00:13:19,502
You can't say that or you will go straight to hell.

164
00:13:20,275 --> 00:13:22,640
He is the master so he can't be guilty.

165
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,960
We are the servant and we need to accept that.

166
00:13:29,846 --> 00:13:31,040
You need to promise me

167
00:13:31,504 --> 00:13:33,320
that you won't do something like this ever again.

168
00:13:33,728 --> 00:13:36,800
You need to respect him, you hear me?

169
00:13:53,371 --> 00:13:55,680
My dad scolded me because of you, you stupid servant!

170
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:58,500
He sent you to school so you could serve me.

171
00:13:58,521 --> 00:13:59,920
Instead, you chose to be a star.

172
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:03,080
He is the master so he can't be guilty.

173
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:06,440
We are the servant and we need to accept that.

174
00:14:21,531 --> 00:14:22,532
Prince Tinnakorn?

175
00:14:31,256 --> 00:14:32,257
Prince Tinnakorn?

176
00:14:34,424 --> 00:14:36,475
I heard from Euam that your mom flogged you.

177
00:14:37,459 --> 00:14:38,460
I'm worried about you.

178
00:14:41,486 --> 00:14:42,487
I'm fine.

179
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,680
But…

180
00:14:49,659 --> 00:14:50,760
You have a wound?

181
00:14:51,131 --> 00:14:53,920
This is little and it's far from my heart. I'm fine.

182
00:14:55,392 --> 00:14:56,480
It's big.

183
00:14:57,435 --> 00:14:58,600
I'm totally fine.

184
00:15:01,091 --> 00:15:02,092
If you don't believe me, just touch it.

185
00:15:05,944 --> 00:15:08,440
See? I'm fine.

186
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:30,000
Ow!

187
00:15:37,739 --> 00:15:38,740
I…

188
00:15:39,952 --> 00:15:42,440
Are you hurt? I'm sorry.

189
00:15:45,758 --> 00:15:46,759
I'm just teasing you.

190
00:15:47,854 --> 00:15:48,855
Come on.

191
00:15:49,326 --> 00:15:50,327
This is fun.

192
00:15:54,904 --> 00:15:57,280
I brought some salve to put on your wounds.

193
00:16:00,387 --> 00:16:01,388
I…

194
00:16:02,142 --> 00:16:03,143
Come on, let me put it on for you.

195
00:16:04,043 --> 00:16:05,560
I….wait.

196
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:07,480
I can put it on myself.

197
00:16:07,611 --> 00:16:08,880
I can do it for you.

198
00:16:09,899 --> 00:16:11,080
It's okay, Your Highness.

199
00:16:11,718 --> 00:16:13,240
- I can do it.
- Phob!

200
00:16:15,062 --> 00:16:16,063
Don't move.

201
00:16:18,800 --> 00:16:19,801
I'll take off your top.

202
00:16:32,803 --> 00:16:33,804
It stings a little.

203
00:16:34,574 --> 00:16:36,680
Give it to me. I can put it on for you.

204
00:16:47,603 --> 00:16:48,604
It will sting a little.

205
00:17:03,654 --> 00:17:04,655
Is it hurt?

206
00:17:06,523 --> 00:17:07,524
I can take it.

207
00:17:22,747 --> 00:17:23,748
Is it hurt here?

208
00:18:11,528 --> 00:18:12,529
Phob, honey.

209
00:18:27,974 --> 00:18:28,975
What did you say?

210
00:18:29,552 --> 00:18:31,387
You wanted me to punish your son?

211
00:18:32,768 --> 00:18:35,080
Yes, Your Highness. He was guilty

212
00:18:35,822 --> 00:18:37,000
for hurting the master.

213
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:42,910
Nual, it's water under the bridge.

214
00:18:43,144 --> 00:18:46,160
Why are you bringing it up?

215
00:18:46,502 --> 00:18:49,819
Also, Phob didn't mean to hurt him.

216
00:18:50,683 --> 00:18:53,776
But my son was really guilty.

217
00:18:54,715 --> 00:18:56,240
He didn't know his place.

218
00:18:56,826 --> 00:18:58,371
And he became this way

219
00:18:58,952 --> 00:19:00,200
because he was arrogant.

220
00:19:00,952 --> 00:19:03,416
He thought that he's Prince Tinnakorn's favorite.

221
00:19:04,579 --> 00:19:07,760
I think you should refrain him

222
00:19:08,118 --> 00:19:10,027
from taking care of Prince Tinnakorn.

223
00:19:10,464 --> 00:19:12,200
So he'd stop acting like this.

224
00:19:12,534 --> 00:19:14,360
They grew up together

225
00:19:15,502 --> 00:19:18,200
and your son always helps my son.

226
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:20,960
We should let him do his job.

227
00:19:21,280 --> 00:19:21,801
But…

228
00:19:21,886 --> 00:19:25,040
You want us to be mean masters

229
00:19:25,650 --> 00:19:28,168
who bullied the servants?

230
00:19:47,142 --> 00:19:48,143
Mom!

231
00:19:49,392 --> 00:19:50,393
Mom!

232
00:19:51,392 --> 00:19:52,393
Mom!

233
00:19:53,686 --> 00:19:57,080
Why did you ask Prince Vasin that I should stop taking care of his son?

234
00:19:57,518 --> 00:19:58,542
Did you eavesdrop earlier?

235
00:20:00,302 --> 00:20:01,560
I did't mean to eavesdrop.

236
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:04,307
You're getting too close to him.

237
00:20:05,301 --> 00:20:06,520
He is a prince.

238
00:20:06,648 --> 00:20:09,080
- And you're just a servant.
- If he wasn't a prince,

239
00:20:09,297 --> 00:20:10,680
if he had no title,

240
00:20:10,830 --> 00:20:13,630
if we were equal, that was when we could get close to each other?

241
00:20:13,752 --> 00:20:15,000
Shut up.

242
00:20:15,614 --> 00:20:17,000
You will go to hell for this.

243
00:20:17,499 --> 00:20:19,240
Don't say the impossible.

244
00:20:20,198 --> 00:20:21,560
You're a servant

245
00:20:21,968 --> 00:20:23,760
and you should know your place.

246
00:20:24,827 --> 00:20:25,840
From now on,

247
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:29,078
you can't get any closer to Prince Tinnakorn, okay?

248
00:20:30,150 --> 00:20:31,680
I'm sorry, Mom.

249
00:20:32,774 --> 00:20:34,811
As long as he needs me close,

250
00:20:35,067 --> 00:20:36,600
I will stay with him like this.

251
00:20:40,296 --> 00:20:41,297
Fine.

252
00:20:42,387 --> 00:20:44,640
He will study abroad soon.

253
00:20:45,214 --> 00:20:48,320
When it happens, even if he doesn't tell you to go,

254
00:20:48,934 --> 00:20:50,840
you can't follow him there anymore.

255
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:11,200
My dad came back from his business trip to France

256
00:21:11,442 --> 00:21:13,320
so he told me to give you this.

257
00:21:14,120 --> 00:21:16,360
You're so kind, honey.

258
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:19,360
- Make yourself at home.
- Yes, ma'am.

259
00:21:29,635 --> 00:21:34,400
The westerners make such a remarkable perfume.

260
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:37,841
Beautiful gift from a beautiful lady.

261
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:40,280
But the recipient…

262
00:21:40,334 --> 00:21:42,440
is even more beautiful.

263
00:21:44,168 --> 00:21:46,600
Look at you,

264
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:48,720
you've always made jokes right in front of the guests

265
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:52,360
since you were young until now.

266
00:21:55,464 --> 00:21:57,240
Siri, don't go home just yet.

267
00:21:57,800 --> 00:21:59,820
You should wait to meet Tinnakorn.

268
00:22:00,472 --> 00:22:03,256
Tinnakorn and Phob should be back soon.

269
00:22:03,571 --> 00:22:05,160
You should wait to meet him.

270
00:22:06,776 --> 00:22:09,200
That's right, you should stay.

271
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:12,222
Do you like to walk in the garden with me?

272
00:22:13,520 --> 00:22:14,680
Roses just bloom.

273
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:16,641
So pretty.

274
00:22:18,062 --> 00:22:21,902
Chatthorn, if you're free, then you should to back to study.

275
00:22:22,691 --> 00:22:24,243
I met your teachers,

276
00:22:24,467 --> 00:22:26,430
and they said that your grades weren't quite well.

277
00:22:27,006 --> 00:22:28,007
But I...

278
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:54,752
Siri? When did you come here?

279
00:23:08,267 --> 00:23:11,400
Saranrom Club will organize music event next week.

280
00:23:11,960 --> 00:23:14,760
I heard that there are bands from overseas, do you want to come?

281
00:23:15,886 --> 00:23:17,646
Do you normally go to the music events?

282
00:23:18,280 --> 00:23:20,800
I can go to the event

283
00:23:21,281 --> 00:23:24,419
when my dad told me to only.

284
00:23:25,363 --> 00:23:27,043
Why did it up to your dad?

285
00:23:27,704 --> 00:23:29,600
If you want to, you can ask him.

286
00:23:30,443 --> 00:23:32,640
My dad doesn't let me go anywhere.

287
00:23:34,235 --> 00:23:36,920
I can go to places, only when he tells me to.

288
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,440
What about this?

289
00:23:42,319 --> 00:23:44,600
If you want to go, I can ask him for you.

290
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:48,960
You can meet with your friends and join the society.

291
00:23:49,803 --> 00:23:51,300
- Sounds good?
- Yeah.

292
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:54,520
In the next few days,

293
00:23:54,960 --> 00:23:56,960
the Thai Red Cross will organize a big fair.

294
00:23:57,291 --> 00:23:58,920
I think you should visit the fair.

295
00:23:59,403 --> 00:24:01,120
I went there last year and it was so much fun.

296
00:24:01,254 --> 00:24:02,255
Right, Phob?

297
00:24:06,512 --> 00:24:07,513
Yes, sir.

298
00:24:08,747 --> 00:24:09,748
Let's eat.

299
00:24:15,608 --> 00:24:16,609
Dad?

300
00:24:17,342 --> 00:24:20,120
Why did you tell me to go and stop me from hanging out with Siri?

301
00:24:20,342 --> 00:24:21,960
Instead, you let Tin hang out with her.

302
00:24:22,816 --> 00:24:24,022
When did you get close to her?

303
00:24:24,811 --> 00:24:27,515
Tinnakorn is closer to Siri than you are.

304
00:24:28,064 --> 00:24:30,120
You will make them feel awkward.

305
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:32,590
How could it be awkward?

306
00:24:33,214 --> 00:24:36,720
It is obvious that I like her.

307
00:24:37,982 --> 00:24:40,500
I don't like her as a sister

308
00:24:41,331 --> 00:24:43,760
but I see her as a woman.

309
00:24:45,683 --> 00:24:46,720
And I think that

310
00:24:47,971 --> 00:24:49,300
Siri likes me to.

311
00:24:51,870 --> 00:24:53,360
I will talk to you frankly

312
00:24:53,912 --> 00:24:55,440
so you will stop with this nonsense.

313
00:24:56,419 --> 00:24:59,342
Siri's dad and I made an agreement

314
00:24:59,480 --> 00:25:01,320
for Tinnakorn to engage to Siri.

315
00:25:03,027 --> 00:25:04,028
What?

316
00:25:05,422 --> 00:25:07,790
Why would you do that?

317
00:25:08,254 --> 00:25:11,360
You know it well that I like Siri, why didn't you let me?

318
00:25:11,566 --> 00:25:13,680
Because I don't want to be mortified.

319
00:25:15,224 --> 00:25:16,600
Look at you.

320
00:25:16,963 --> 00:25:18,475
You're doing so bad in school

321
00:25:18,643 --> 00:25:19,800
and you are not a decent human being.

322
00:25:20,179 --> 00:25:22,780
The whole city know about

323
00:25:22,800 --> 00:25:24,300
you getting in a fight with people.

324
00:25:24,875 --> 00:25:27,451
What kind of parents would want you to marry their daughters?

325
00:25:35,331 --> 00:25:36,680
This is not fair.

326
00:25:40,739 --> 00:25:43,160
You've never given me anything good.

327
00:25:44,816 --> 00:25:47,600
You've always given Tin something good.

328
00:25:47,617 --> 00:25:51,000
- England and Siri. What about me?
- Chatthorn!

329
00:25:52,704 --> 00:25:54,800
Stop thinking about your love life already

330
00:25:55,083 --> 00:25:56,760
and focus on your study.

331
00:25:58,432 --> 00:26:00,742
And don't compare yourself to your brother,

332
00:26:01,387 --> 00:26:03,400
you can't even compare yourself to Phob.

333
00:26:18,390 --> 00:26:20,120
Go back to study.

334
00:26:28,878 --> 00:26:29,879
Phob!

335
00:26:30,739 --> 00:26:31,760
Why are you here?

336
00:26:33,634 --> 00:26:35,406
Princess Siri is gone?

337
00:26:35,806 --> 00:26:38,080
Yeah, I just sent her off.

338
00:26:39,971 --> 00:26:40,972
I see.

339
00:26:41,928 --> 00:26:44,480
So now you have time for me.

340
00:26:46,608 --> 00:26:48,960
What is wrong with you? Phob?

341
00:26:50,875 --> 00:26:51,876
Are you sick?

342
00:26:59,904 --> 00:27:01,760
I saw you enjoy talking to her.

343
00:27:03,675 --> 00:27:04,840
Do you like her?

344
00:27:09,888 --> 00:27:11,456
I feel bad for her.

345
00:27:12,656 --> 00:27:14,310
She needs to follow her dad's orders,

346
00:27:14,544 --> 00:27:15,862
she can't do anything on her own.

347
00:27:16,619 --> 00:27:19,003
I adore her

348
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:24,880
but as a sister.

349
00:27:35,774 --> 00:27:37,040
So what is wrong with you?

350
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:40,761
What's with the grumpy face?

351
00:27:45,491 --> 00:27:48,400
Tin! Are you happy now? Why are you doing this?

352
00:27:50,632 --> 00:27:53,240
Move, you filthy servant!

353
00:27:56,891 --> 00:28:00,080
Both of you must be laughing at me, right?

354
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:02,574
You know it well that I like Siri.

355
00:28:02,734 --> 00:28:03,960
What are you talking about?

356
00:28:05,912 --> 00:28:07,360
Why did you bring Siri into this?

357
00:28:10,718 --> 00:28:12,100
Stop acting so innocent already.

358
00:28:13,670 --> 00:28:15,400
Dad wanted you to be engaged to Siri.

359
00:28:17,787 --> 00:28:18,788
What?

360
00:28:30,110 --> 00:28:31,520
It's true what he said.

361
00:28:32,296 --> 00:28:33,400
What is your problem?

362
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:36,081
I…

363
00:28:37,059 --> 00:28:38,800
I don't love her like that.

364
00:28:41,539 --> 00:28:43,320
We're like brother and sister.

365
00:28:45,723 --> 00:28:47,680
It's not always about love.

366
00:28:48,683 --> 00:28:50,080
It's about suitability.

367
00:28:52,691 --> 00:28:55,760
- But I don't love Ruethaisiri.
- Or you love someone else?

368
00:29:03,142 --> 00:29:04,360
Who's that girl?

369
00:29:07,606 --> 00:29:08,607
It's okay.

370
00:29:10,607 --> 00:29:12,760
I don't care who she is.

371
00:29:14,152 --> 00:29:17,040
You can just marry Ruethaisiri as your first wife.

372
00:29:17,976 --> 00:29:20,520
So she can help taking care of the palace.

373
00:29:22,418 --> 00:29:23,840
You're a great man,

374
00:29:24,626 --> 00:29:26,480
you can have 4-5 wives

375
00:29:26,775 --> 00:29:28,360
and I think you can take care of them all.

376
00:29:46,435 --> 00:29:47,640
Soon,

377
00:29:47,784 --> 00:29:49,800
our palace will hear good news

378
00:29:49,840 --> 00:29:51,920
from Prince Tinnakorn and Princess Ruethaisiri.

379
00:29:53,214 --> 00:29:54,264
You knew about this?

380
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:57,120
Prince Chat yelled so loud like that,

381
00:29:57,262 --> 00:29:58,440
everyone heard about it.

382
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:06,400
But Prince Tin doesn't love her like that.

383
00:30:07,376 --> 00:30:09,248
He just adores her as a sister.

384
00:30:11,472 --> 00:30:12,859
His relationship

385
00:30:13,515 --> 00:30:14,680
is none of your business.

386
00:30:18,587 --> 00:30:19,760
He is a master

387
00:30:20,315 --> 00:30:22,200
the servants like us can't be involved.

388
00:30:23,056 --> 00:30:24,600
But he shouldn't be forced to be into this.

389
00:30:26,032 --> 00:30:27,033
He should be the one

390
00:30:27,822 --> 00:30:29,840
who decides on his relationship.

391
00:30:33,315 --> 00:30:35,720
That's none of your business.

392
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,920
He is a master

393
00:30:39,827 --> 00:30:41,360
and he has his duties to fulfill.

394
00:30:42,627 --> 00:30:44,120
Our duties

395
00:30:45,155 --> 00:30:47,720
are to taking care of him and be greatful.

396
00:30:48,283 --> 00:30:49,284
Didn't you see?

397
00:30:50,592 --> 00:30:51,800
This is me trying to give back to him.

398
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:55,878
I want to help him and make him happy.

399
00:30:56,776 --> 00:30:58,371
I don't want him to marry someone he doesn’t love.

400
00:31:00,574 --> 00:31:01,600
Are you sure about that?

401
00:31:09,446 --> 00:31:12,160
You're not thinking of him more than just a master, are you?

402
00:31:20,360 --> 00:31:22,161
- Mom! I..
- Listen to me carefully.

403
00:31:25,635 --> 00:31:27,360
No matter what your thoughts are,

404
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,480
they have to stop now.

405
00:31:32,547 --> 00:31:34,440
Don't drag him to your level.

406
00:31:35,315 --> 00:31:36,480
He is a master

407
00:31:37,072 --> 00:31:38,320
and we are only servants.

408
00:31:39,168 --> 00:31:41,312
We can only respect him

409
00:31:41,558 --> 00:31:43,240
as one of royal family members.

410
00:31:48,523 --> 00:31:49,524
If one day,

411
00:31:49,654 --> 00:31:51,760
you think of him more than a master and servant.

412
00:31:52,619 --> 00:31:53,620
You will be the one

413
00:31:54,955 --> 00:31:56,560
who will taint his reputation.

414
00:32:58,091 --> 00:33:01,092
♪ A mischievious ♪

415
00:33:03,312 --> 00:33:05,560
♪ and hard-working ♪

416
00:33:10,739 --> 00:33:13,200
♪ man named Ngoh ♪

417
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:22,400
♪ He saw a daughter ♪

418
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:32,800
♪ of a ruler. ♪

419
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:42,680
♪ Her skin is glowing ♪

420
00:33:48,611 --> 00:33:53,520
♪ like the moon. ♪

421
00:34:40,032 --> 00:34:43,760
Prince Yai's live performance is so great.

422
00:34:46,784 --> 00:34:50,040
His team is the most popular in the city.

423
00:34:51,198 --> 00:34:53,843
My grandma has booked the team for months.

424
00:35:03,358 --> 00:35:04,359
Scoot over.

425
00:35:06,302 --> 00:35:07,303
Move your leg.

426
00:35:08,595 --> 00:35:09,596
Move your leg.

427
00:35:09,828 --> 00:35:10,880
One leg at a time.

428
00:35:11,128 --> 00:35:13,480
- Move my leg?
- Follow me. Watch me.

429
00:35:14,851 --> 00:35:17,920
One at a time like this, follow my lead.

430
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,760
Now speed up! Speed up!

431
00:35:22,768 --> 00:35:23,769
Look at me!

432
00:35:25,350 --> 00:35:27,040
- Do you know what it is?
- Like what?

433
00:35:31,246 --> 00:35:32,247
Like Ngoh!

434
00:35:35,011 --> 00:35:36,012
Smile.

435
00:35:38,755 --> 00:35:40,680
You saw me as an ugly and dirty-looking guy, didn't you?

436
00:35:41,998 --> 00:35:42,999
If that's the case,

437
00:35:43,912 --> 00:35:44,760
from now on,

438
00:35:45,726 --> 00:35:47,720
I won't help you study anymore.

439
00:35:48,734 --> 00:35:49,960
Stop sulking already.

440
00:35:51,715 --> 00:35:54,792
I mean you look like Ngoh when he shows his real self.

441
00:36:07,382 --> 00:36:09,920
Ngoh's skin is covered with gold.

442
00:36:13,128 --> 00:36:14,254
But I'm just a servant,

443
00:36:15,886 --> 00:36:17,270
I am nothing like him.

444
00:36:21,632 --> 00:36:25,600
Nobody would toss me a garland like she did to him.

445
00:36:44,840 --> 00:36:45,841
No garland

446
00:36:50,755 --> 00:36:52,560
but you can have a cotton rose.

447
00:37:09,246 --> 00:37:10,560
So it means that

448
00:37:13,774 --> 00:37:17,080
you choose me.

449
00:37:27,219 --> 00:37:28,360
Is that right?

450
00:37:49,478 --> 00:37:51,240
I'm hungry.

451
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,761
Let's find something to eat in the kitchen.

452
00:38:13,571 --> 00:38:15,320
Don't drag him to your level.

453
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:17,321
He is a master

454
00:38:18,121 --> 00:38:19,240
and we are only servants.

455
00:38:20,190 --> 00:38:22,288
We can only respect him

456
00:38:22,518 --> 00:38:24,200
as one of royal family members.

457
00:38:26,448 --> 00:38:27,449
If one day,

458
00:38:27,616 --> 00:38:29,680
you think of him more than a master and servant.

459
00:38:29,967 --> 00:38:32,968
You will be the one who will taint his reputation.

460
00:39:04,835 --> 00:39:05,836
Nual.

461
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:08,480
Where is Phob? It's about time to go to school?

462
00:39:09,091 --> 00:39:11,854
Well, he left since early morning.

463
00:39:12,120 --> 00:39:13,800
He said that he'd study before class first.

464
00:39:14,299 --> 00:39:16,300
What? He normally waited for me.

465
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,800
Why did he leave first?

466
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:20,120
I don't know, Your Highness.

467
00:39:20,808 --> 00:39:22,480
But it is better this way.

468
00:39:23,203 --> 00:39:25,731
He is a servant, you should let him go to school by himself.

469
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,841
[Royal Pages School]

470
00:39:48,278 --> 00:39:49,279
Kamol?

471
00:39:50,219 --> 00:39:51,600
Have you seen Phobthee?

472
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:54,680
I haven't. He's normally around you all the time.

473
00:39:56,251 --> 00:39:57,880
Let's go, we don't want to be late.

474
00:39:58,251 --> 00:39:59,252
- Let's go.
- Come on.

475
00:40:22,403 --> 00:40:23,880
I want to play soccer next week.

476
00:40:24,128 --> 00:40:25,320
Sure, you want to join?

477
00:40:25,382 --> 00:40:26,480
- Sure.
- You're joining us?

478
00:40:26,502 --> 00:40:29,000
- We need Weerapon to join the team.
- He needs to come.

479
00:40:29,211 --> 00:40:31,840
He's so good at blocking.

480
00:40:32,040 --> 00:40:33,080
- So great.
- Phob.

481
00:40:35,232 --> 00:40:36,233
There you are.

482
00:40:37,056 --> 00:40:38,520
Let's get back home. The driver is waiting.

483
00:40:44,571 --> 00:40:45,680
I have to run some errands.

484
00:40:47,772 --> 00:40:48,920
I think I will go home by myself.

485
00:40:51,646 --> 00:40:52,960
You can go home, Your Highness.

486
00:41:01,352 --> 00:41:02,353
What's wrong?

487
00:41:03,822 --> 00:41:04,960
I'm not mad at you.

488
00:41:07,438 --> 00:41:08,440
I'm just a servant.

489
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:11,600
- How could I be mad at the master?
- Enough with the master and servant.

490
00:41:14,792 --> 00:41:15,960
I know!

491
00:41:16,563 --> 00:41:19,100
You still think about Chat's insults, don't you?

492
00:41:21,059 --> 00:41:22,640
It has nothing to do with him.

493
00:41:23,560 --> 00:41:24,841
Then what is it about?

494
00:41:29,142 --> 00:41:30,143
I..

495
00:41:31,013 --> 00:41:32,840
Have I offended you?

496
00:41:35,627 --> 00:41:37,120
Can you tell me?

497
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:41,000
I could have done something and I didn't know it, so tell me.

498
00:41:42,902 --> 00:41:44,280
If I know, I won't do it again.

499
00:41:46,048 --> 00:41:48,240
But you refuse to tell me anything.

500
00:41:50,019 --> 00:41:52,040
I don't know what to do.

501
00:41:57,907 --> 00:41:59,960
Phob! Phob!

502
00:42:01,722 --> 00:42:05,200
Hey, what is the name of the female vendor in front of the school?

503
00:42:06,192 --> 00:42:07,520
The one that you helped her the other day.

504
00:42:09,792 --> 00:42:12,960
(In unison) Saijai.

505
00:42:13,638 --> 00:42:16,040
Here, she wanted me to give you some snacks.

506
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,560
You're quite something.

507
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:21,400
That Saijai who is pretty with nice skin, right?

508
00:42:21,694 --> 00:42:23,840
Whoa! Aren't you a charmer?

509
00:42:24,008 --> 00:42:25,520
Our friend is quite something, isn't he?

510
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:29,280
Hey! There is a new bar at Charoen Krung.

511
00:42:29,451 --> 00:42:30,520
Should we give it a try?

512
00:42:30,571 --> 00:42:32,600
- Let's go.
- I'll buy Phob some drinks.

513
00:42:33,046 --> 00:42:35,400
He tutored us until we passed the test.

514
00:42:37,808 --> 00:42:39,760
- You should come, Your Highness.
- Please come.

515
00:42:45,304 --> 00:42:46,305
Come on. Let's go.

516
00:42:46,755 --> 00:42:48,320
Don't be late.

517
00:42:56,208 --> 00:42:57,640
I think you should go home first.

518
00:43:07,184 --> 00:43:08,400
Cheers!

519
00:43:19,357 --> 00:43:20,640
You shouldn't be drinking too much.

520
00:43:23,536 --> 00:43:25,334
We're at the bar so we need to drink some liquor.

521
00:43:26,070 --> 00:43:27,800
You expected me to have some desserts?

522
00:43:29,328 --> 00:43:31,800
That's right. Having some desserts? Cheers!

523
00:43:34,048 --> 00:43:37,000
You're right, Your Highness.

524
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:39,800
We're not at Saijai's stall selling desserts.

525
00:43:44,104 --> 00:43:46,800
Among all of us, I think Phob

526
00:43:46,926 --> 00:43:48,480
will be the first with a girlfriend.

527
00:43:48,707 --> 00:43:51,240
Of course, Saiji has such beautiful eyes.

528
00:43:51,720 --> 00:43:53,000
And she flirted with you.

529
00:43:53,219 --> 00:43:56,520
As a real man, you should reciprocate.

530
00:43:58,040 --> 00:43:59,041
Shut up!

531
00:44:22,619 --> 00:44:24,640
Hey! I lost the bet and I still need to buy you drinks?

532
00:44:24,827 --> 00:44:27,760
You can have another round to make it up next time.

533
00:44:32,910 --> 00:44:34,640
I told you that you shouldn't be drinking too much.

534
00:44:39,107 --> 00:44:40,160
Did you watch me?

535
00:44:42,342 --> 00:44:43,400
How could you ask me that?

536
00:44:45,078 --> 00:44:46,560
You should know it well that

537
00:44:47,712 --> 00:44:50,360
I care for you every day.

538
00:44:51,966 --> 00:44:53,000
Well, that was before.

539
00:44:55,555 --> 00:44:58,560
Now you could care more about that Saijai.

540
00:44:59,480 --> 00:45:00,481
Your Highness.

541
00:45:00,814 --> 00:45:02,491
You should care for her.

542
00:45:03,915 --> 00:45:07,080
And you can forget what you said about

543
00:45:09,056 --> 00:45:10,057
being my Phob.

544
00:45:24,423 --> 00:45:25,880
Enough with your sarcasm already.

545
00:45:28,843 --> 00:45:30,240
You should know it well that

546
00:45:30,944 --> 00:45:34,240
I meant what I said.

547
00:45:35,936 --> 00:45:38,360
I will be your loyal servant,

548
00:45:39,256 --> 00:45:40,320
always have and always will.

549
00:45:41,187 --> 00:45:42,280
Why did you avoid me?

550
00:45:44,003 --> 00:45:45,320
You've been avoiding me all day.

551
00:45:46,227 --> 00:45:47,480
What did I do?

552
00:45:50,099 --> 00:45:51,600
It's not your fault.

553
00:45:51,918 --> 00:45:54,160
So you accepted the fact that you avoided seeing me.

554
00:45:55,264 --> 00:45:56,832
Why didn't you tell me?

555
00:45:59,312 --> 00:46:01,387
We've talked about everything since we were young.

556
00:46:01,760 --> 00:46:04,600
Did you know that you hurt my feeling when you acted like that?

557
00:46:06,761 --> 00:46:07,762
You know?

558
00:46:10,366 --> 00:46:11,367
Something

559
00:46:12,398 --> 00:46:13,560
can't be said.

560
00:46:14,648 --> 00:46:15,880
Because I'm worried that

561
00:46:16,942 --> 00:46:18,400
you wouldn't understand

562
00:46:19,736 --> 00:46:21,120
and you could hate me.

563
00:46:25,259 --> 00:46:26,260
Just try to say it.

564
00:46:31,136 --> 00:46:32,137
Actually…

565
00:46:37,611 --> 00:46:38,612
I..

566
00:46:40,422 --> 00:46:41,423
I…

567
00:46:52,342 --> 00:46:53,760
I think we should go home

568
00:46:55,592 --> 00:46:56,600
so you can rest.

569
00:47:21,390 --> 00:47:23,120
You should have let me fall.

570
00:47:25,192 --> 00:47:27,280
So I'll get used to it when you're not around.

571
00:47:28,080 --> 00:47:29,081
Your Highness,

572
00:47:30,360 --> 00:47:32,680
it's not like I wanted to give you cold shoulder or ignored you.

573
00:47:34,240 --> 00:47:36,800
I was just worried that if I said it,

574
00:47:37,307 --> 00:47:38,440
you would hate me.

575
00:47:41,424 --> 00:47:42,800
Why don't you try to say it?

576
00:47:44,555 --> 00:47:47,600
I promiose you that no matter what you say or do,

577
00:47:47,620 --> 00:47:48,840
I will not hate or be mad at you.

578
00:47:51,150 --> 00:47:52,151
I promise.

579
00:48:31,024 --> 00:48:33,500
Who are they? What are they doing in the back?

580
00:48:51,894 --> 00:48:53,120
I saw it.

581
00:48:53,366 --> 00:48:55,160
That night, at the back of the bar,

582
00:48:55,200 --> 00:48:56,300
I saw what you two did.

583
00:48:56,827 --> 00:48:58,000
There you are.

584
00:49:00,700 --> 00:49:04,040
I saw Phob and Tin ran to the maid's quarters.

585
00:49:05,080 --> 00:49:07,880
I will be your Phob

586
00:49:08,560 --> 00:49:09,561
forever.

